{"tid":1278042,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"((急))有貓貓需要幫手 有冇九龍區人可以幫手!!","createTime":"2019-07-02T10:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T15:50:46.000Z","uid":65273,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"413f7f511e72e071e322fb27a37b21364437ac55","tid":1278042,"uid":65273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:47:02.000Z","msg":"件事係咁 <br />\n<br />\n我朋友係啲free電器group到 聯絡到一位女士有我朋友想要既電器 一上到去 發現有隻貓係入面 好瘦 糧兜已經冇野食 地下有屎 眼矇矇咁 但屋內冇人 <br />\n<br />\n我朋友有撩下隻貓 但貓貓冇乜反應 佢拎左電器番到屋企覺得唔對路 驚隻貓會出事 就Wtsapp問下果個人隻貓係咪唔要<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果佢真係咁樣答 但我朋友and我最後都係搵唔到朋友可以去幫手 而我同朋友都係養唔到 所以上黎連登搵巴絲求救  有冇有經驗養貓既人可以幫手?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲可以幫手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以tg 我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <a href=\"https://t.me/uron9jai\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Furon9jai&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=d1dfc3c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/uron9jai</a>"},{"pid":"bcf53b60159273e5f3612199f38408493a2d13aa","tid":1278042,"uid":65273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:48:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d7fd3f73aed5c2244b2e6dc6ff67acadfe1048b","tid":1278042,"uid":65273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:51:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62387dec1ce847992f5bfe8bdc93b7099ccc